Global Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil Market Insights
Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil Market Overview
The global Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil market has seen remarkable growth, valued at approximately USD 1.4 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 2.3 billion by 2030, expanding at a CAGR of 9.0% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for natural and plant-based ingredients in the cosmetic, food, and pharmaceutical industries has significantly contributed to the market's growth. The oil is known for its nutritional, anti-inflammatory, and moisturizing properties, which have boosted its adoption across various applications. These dynamics are fueling investments in cannabis sativa oil production, driving market expansion globally.

